name: Mixedmodels-misc
tagline: miscellaneous materials for mixed models, mostly in R
body: This repository provides a variety of resources I've written, or compiled, about mixed models; the focus is on the tools I help develop and maintain (the `lme4`, `glmmTMB`, and `glmmADMB` packages for R).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
